There are several earthworks in our area. One of which is the site of a royal hunting lodge. This lodge now no longer exists but the site is marked by several mounds.{(Section 7)}.
Also just below}Ashurt lodge is another earthwork which consists of a motte and bailey. {(Secion 11) }
Also near the campsite is an earthwork of unknown origin but is thought to be that of a large house or building. {(Section 5)}
Also in our area there are many tumuli. These are mainly situated around sections 9,10 and 11.
